@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #2F4F4F
skinparam DefaultTextAlignment center

left to right direction

title C4 - Arquitectura Rate Limiting S2 (policy en NGINX Ingress)

actor "k6 S2 runner" as k6

cloud "Edge Layer" {
  component "NGINX Ingress\n(realistic-gateway)" as gw
  component "Rate Limiter" as rl
}

node "Namespace mubench-real" {
  component "auth-service" as auth
  component "api-service" as api
  component "data-service" as data
  database "postgres" as db
}

k6 --> auth : HTTP NodePort 30184 (/login)
k6 --> api : HTTP NodePort 30181 (/profile,/users)

gw --> rl : evaluacion por tasa (rps/rpm)
rl --> auth : permitido o 429
rl --> api : permitido o 429

api --> data : HTTP 8080
data --> db : TCP 5432

note right of rl
C4/baseline:
- sin limite

C4/moderate:
- ~1200 rpm (20 rps)
- afecta carga alta

C4/strict:
- ~300 rpm (5 rps)
- puede generar 429 si el trafico entra por ingress

Nota S2 final:
- La politica se configura en NGINX Ingress
- El benchmark se ejecuta via NodePort HTTP
end note

@enduml
